reviewText: Arrived in a great time. Worked perfectly would buy again. Recommended to friends

Same problem as the other Shimmer videos, good overall matches but poor quality. It's viewable but the quality even for an independent wrestling company is somehow bad. The best thing about this video is the fact you are able to watch some female wrestlers otherwise unknown to the public unless they made it big into WWE or TNA but since the women's division on those big companies is more eye candy than wrestling this video makes for less gimmick and more wrestling, you get good looking female wrestlers as well (and others not so much) but the main thing here is wrestling. Recommended for wrestling fans who want to see something different than usual.
